# Analyse, interpretatie en bruikbaarheid {background-image="https://thumbs.dreamstime.com/b/medical-tech-science-ai-health-technology-surgical-doctor-telehealth-telemedicine-iot-global-healthcare-service-210434732.jpg" background-size="cover" background-opacity="0.5"}

